00:41:37.440 --> 00:41:40.080
They seemed to find this
example pretty humorous.

00:41:40.080 --> 00:41:42.230
No offense to anyone
in here named John.

00:41:42.230 --> 00:41:43.730
I didn't meet anyone
named John yet,

00:41:43.730 --> 00:41:46.540
but-- So it obviously
doesn't apply to you

00:41:46.540 --> 00:41:48.010
