they're on the large side,

00:41:57.840 --> 00:42:02.590
I would exaggerate those as
being gigantic Dumbo-like ears,

00:42:02.590 --> 00:42:04.630
swinging from the
side of his head.

00:42:04.630 --> 00:42:06.060
And since the
name's John, I might

00:42:06.060 --> 00:42:08.630
put a toilet bowl
flushing in each ear,

00:42:08.630 --> 00:42:09.930
as in going to the john.

00:42:13.990 --> 00:42:16.320
The news anchors, they
couldn't stop laughing.

00:42:16.320 --> 00:42:19.830
And then actually, that clip
also made it on VH1's best week

00:42:19.830 --> 00:42:23.210
