very well in your minds.

00:42:29.290 --> 00:42:31.350
The next time you see
the guy, instantly you're

00:42:31.350 --> 00:42:35.040
going to know that
his name is John.

00:42:35.040 --> 00:42:38.150
I know it sounds
a little unusual,

00:42:38.150 --> 00:42:44.030
